        "description": "\"This game in my honest opinion is a hidden gem. \" - TruGamer4Realz\n\n\"It was a nice surprise and really enjoy it. - Welshgamervr\n\n\" I am SO surprised there isn't more reviews! - langsvr1111\n\n2 billion downloads mobile hit comes to VR!\n\nStep into the world of CookieRun! Play as GingerBrave, a freshly baked 15cm cookie armed with a candy cane and the power of friendship. Embark on a big adventure from a small perspective. \n\nTo escape the Witch's castle, you'll have to defeat The Darkest Lord and his army, \n the magical creatures and monsters. But fear not, you won't be alone! Gather cookie companions and pets to accompany you on your journey and aid you in battle. \n\nBecome the legendary GingerBrave, and bring light to The Darkest Night!\n\nFEATURES\n\n• Experience 11 uniquely themed spaces, from human-sized areas like the oven, Bakery, Incubation Chamber, Auditorium and Forge to cookie-scaled spots like Gnome Square, Tunnel, Armory and Lava Mine. Discover them all!\n\n• Dive into intense battles! Combat diverse foes, each with unique personalities. Wield 3 melee weapons with 4 elemental variations and 3 slingshots with 5 elemental bullets. Test your skills!\n\n• Full of VR-only interactions!\nDrive mining carts, yank out mandrakes, take control of a colossal Franken Cookie, dodge cats, shatter barriers, tug on a lizard's tail, and so much more!",
